{"ja486:0.1":"Jataka ","ja486:0.2":"Pakinnakanipata ","ja486:0.3":"Salikedaravagga ","ja486:0.4":"3. Mahaukkusajataka ","ja486:1.1":"“Ukka cilaca bandhanti dipe, ","ja486:1.2":"Paja mamam khaditum patthayanti; ","ja486:1.3":"Mittam sahayanca vadehi senaka, ","ja486:1.4":"Acikkha natibyasanam dijanam”. ","ja486:2.1":"“Dijo dijanam pavarosi pakkhima, ","ja486:2.2":"Ukkusaraja saranam tam upema; ","ja486:2.3":"Paja mamam khaditum patthayanti, ","ja486:2.4":"Ludda cilaca bhava me sukhaya”. ","ja486:3.1":"“Mittam sahayanca karonti pandita, ","ja486:3.2":"Kale akale sukhamesamana; ","ja486:3.3":"Karomi te senaka etamattham, ","ja486:3.4":"Ariyo hi ariyassa karoti kiccam”. ","ja486:4.1":"“Yam hoti kiccam anukampakena, ","ja486:4.2":"Ariyassa ariyena katam tayidam; ","ja486:4.3":"Attanurakkhi bhava ma adayhi, ","ja486:4.4":"Lacchama putte tayi jivamane”. ","ja486:5.1":"“Taveva rakkhavaranam karonto, ","ja486:5.2":"Sarirabhedapi na santasami; ","ja486:5.3":"Karonti heke sakhinam sakharo, ","ja486:5.4":"Panam cajanta satamesa dhammo”. ","ja486:6.1":"“Sudukkaram kammamakasi, ","ja486:6.2":"andajayam vihangamo; ","ja486:6.3":"Atthaya kuraro putte, ","ja486:6.4":"addharatte anagate”. ","ja486:7.1":"“Cutapi heke khalita sakammuna, ","ja486:7.2":"Mittanukampaya patitthahanti; ","ja486:7.3":"Putta mamatta gatimagatosmi, ","ja486:7.4":"Attham caretho mama varicara”. ","ja486:8.1":"“Dhanena dhannena ca attana ca, ","ja486:8.2":"Mittam sahayanca karonti pandita; ","ja486:8.3":"Karomi te senaka etamattham, ","ja486:8.4":"Ariyo hi ariyassa karoti kiccam”. ","ja486:9.1":"“Appossukko tata tuvam nisida, ","ja486:9.2":"Putto pitu carati atthacariyam; ","ja486:9.3":"Aham carissami tavetamattham, ","ja486:9.4":"Senassa putte paritayamano”. ","ja486:10.1":"“Addha hi tata satamesa dhammo, ","ja486:10.2":"Putto pitu yam care atthacariyam; ","ja486:10.3":"Appeva mam disvana pavaddhakayam, ","ja486:10.4":"Senassa putta na vihethayeyyum”. ","ja486:11.1":"“Pasu manussa migavirasettha, ","ja486:11.2":"Bhayattita setthamupabbajanti; ","ja486:11.3":"Putta mamatta gatimagatosmi, ","ja486:11.4":"Tvam nosi raja bhava me sukhaya”. ","ja486:12.1":"“Karomi te senaka etamattham, ","ja486:12.2":"Ayami te tam disatam vadhaya; ","ja486:12.3":"Kathanhi vinnu pahu sampajano, ","ja486:12.4":"Na vayame attajanassa guttiya”. ","ja486:13.1":"“Mittanca kayiratha suhadayanca, ","ja486:13.2":"Ayiranca kayiratha sukhagamaya; ","ja486:13.3":"Nivatthakocova sarebhihantva, ","ja486:13.4":"Modama puttehi samangibhuta. ","ja486:14.1":"Sakamittassa kammena, ","ja486:14.2":"sahayassapalayino; ","ja486:14.3":"Kujantamupakujanti, ","ja486:14.4":"lomasa hadayangamam. ","ja486:15.1":"Mittam sahayam adhigamma pandito, ","ja486:15.2":"So bhunjati putta pasum dhanam va; ","ja486:15.3":"Ahanca putta ca pati ca mayham, ","ja486:15.4":"Mittanukampaya samangibhuta. ","ja486:16.1":"Rajavata suravata ca attho, ","ja486:16.2":"Sampannasakhissa bhavanti hete; ","ja486:16.3":"So mittava yasava uggatatto, ","ja486:16.4":"Asmimdhaloke modati kamakami. ","ja486:17.1":"Karaniyani mittani, ","ja486:17.2":"daliddenapi senaka; ","ja486:17.3":"Passa mittanukampaya, ","ja486:17.4":"samaggamha sanatake. ","ja486:18.1":"Surena balavantena, ","ja486:18.2":"yo mitte kurute dijo; ","ja486:18.3":"Evam so sukhito hoti, ","ja486:18.4":"yathaham tvanca senakati”. ","ja486:19.1":"Mahaukkusajatakam tatiyam. "}